The girl above is no expert —but she finds she, too, can ride the long
rollers into Waikiki Beach and make the dream of a lifetime come true!
With trade winds in your hair
and work 2500 miles behind_
You're in HAWAII, where there is no winter, 10 hours
after you leave the West Coast on Pan American's deluxe
"Strato" Clipper* service -"THE PRESIDENT"
You need no passport to fly to Hawaii because it's U.S. soil.
But you do need facts to plan your trip-facts and costs.
So, in addition to its famous $1 fact book about foreign
travel,
"New Horizons'*, Pan American will mail you two
new folders on Hawaii without extra charge. Folder #1
contains exciting Kodachrome photos of the
Hawaiian Islands and a beautiful map
printed in full color. Folder #2 contains
details of many inclusive Pan Am
Holidays ranging from $333.25 for
1 week to $530.70 for 3 weeks.
Clip coupon now.
*Trade-Marks, Reg. U. S. Pat. Off.
Erices west at oment or its or u.s.
add transporteno
- Box Ame, an or 17, N. Dept. NH-30
Enclosed is one dollar. Please mail me post-
paid, my copy of "New Horizons" plus my
two copies of your new Hawaii folders.
PAN AMERICAN
